kv = {'element_name': 'cntry_name', 'element_desc':
    'ISO standard country name', 'element_type': 'string', 'element_len': 40}
assert self.md.element_tools.setter(**kv) != 0
assert len(self.md.element_tools.lister()) == 2
assert self.md.element_tools.getter(element_name='cntry_name'
    ).element_len == 40
kv['element_len'] = 100
assert self.md.element_tools.setter(**kv) == 0
assert len(self.md.element_tools.lister()) == 2
assert self.md.element_tools.getter(element_name='cntry_name'
    ).element_len == 100
